ResourceTokenRegistry
├── mint
│   ├── when caller is not a registered minter
│   │   └── it should revert with NotAuthorizedMinter
│   ├── when token type is invalid (not 0x01, 0x02, 0x03)
│   │   └── it should revert with InvalidTokenType
│   ├── when caller is a registered minter and type is valid
│   │   ├── it should auto-generate a unique token ID
│   │   ├── it should set balance to 1
│   │   ├── it should store creator as msg.sender
│   │   ├── it should store metadata
│   │   ├── it should emit TokenCreated event
│   │   ├── it should emit Transfer event
│   │   └── it should increment lastId for that type
├── burn
│   ├── when caller is not the creator of the token
│   │   └── it should revert with NotTokenCreator
│   ├── when target has no balance
│   │   └── it should revert with InsufficientBalance
│   └── when caller is the creator and target has balance
│       ├── it should set balance to 0
│       └── it should emit Transfer event
├── transfer
│   ├── when caller is not the creator of the token
│   │   └── it should revert with NotTokenCreator
│   ├── when caller is the creator
│   │   ├── when sender has insufficient balance
│   │   │   └── it should revert with InsufficientBalance
│   │   └── when valid
│   │       ├── it should move the token
│   │       └── it should emit Transfer event
├── transferFrom
│   ├── when caller is not the creator of the token
│   │   └── it should revert with NotTokenCreator
│   ├── when caller is the creator
│   │   ├── when sender has insufficient balance
│   │   │   └── it should revert with InsufficientBalance
│   │   └── when valid
│   │       ├── it should move the token
│   │       └── it should emit Transfer event
├── approve
│   └── it should revert with ApprovalsDisabled
├── setOperator
│   └── it should revert with ApprovalsDisabled
├── registerMinter
│   ├── when caller is not the owner
│   │   └── it should revert with NotOwner
│   └── when caller is the owner
│       ├── it should set isMinter to true
│       └── it should emit MinterRegistered event
├── tokenMetadata
│   └── it should return stored metadata for the token id
├── creator
│   └── it should return the creator address for the token id
├── lastId
│   └── it should return the mint counter for a given token type
├── tokenType
│   └── it should return the lowest 8 bits of the token id
├── isPermission
│   ├── when lowest 8 bits == 0x01
│   │   └── it should return true
│   └── otherwise
│       └── it should return false
├── isResponsibility
│   ├── when lowest 8 bits == 0x02
│   │   └── it should return true
│   └── otherwise
│       └── it should return false
└── isDirective
    ├── when lowest 8 bits == 0x03
    │   └── it should return true
    └── otherwise
        └── it should return false
